description: This is the function signature for current:returnObject used by onGetObjects and onRetrieveObjects. Calling this directly will throw a 'Do not call directly' error.

parameters.description: This is the object to return.
parameters.name: object

parameters.description: If this is present and true, the object will be mapped its mapped adaptor's object type to the model adaptor's object type.
parameters.name: userData

returns.brief: true if no more objects can be returned
returns.description: This will return true if no more objects can be returned for any reason including a limit exceeded, connection closed, or server stopping.
